MPU --> ESP32 connection layout 

VCC and GND --> 3V3 and GND

SCL --> P22

SDA --> P21

---------------------------------
(For ServoX)


ESP32 --> Servo 

VCC and GND --> 5V and GND

P13 --> PWM

__________________________________

(For ServoY)

ESP32 --> Servo 

VCC and GND --> 5V and GND

P14 --> PWM
